Package: age-api
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, helper-scripts
Description: Local age bracket storage and query helper (age signaling)
 age-api provides a minimal local mechanism to store an age bracket and query it
 for age-signaling use cases.
 .
 The age-api-query tool outputs a machine-readable
 age bracket number on stdout and a human-readable description on stderr.
 .
 See also: https://www.kicksecure.com/wiki/age-api
